meanings.definition: A heterocyclic organic compound consisting of a benzene ring fused to a coumaran (dihydrobenzofuran) ring system.
meanings.english_definition: A heterocyclic organic compound consisting of a benzene ring fused to a coumaran (dihydrobenzofuran) ring system.

etymology.value: Derived from 'benzene' + 'coumarin' + '-an' (suffix indicating a saturated or partially saturated compound).
